---
title: Laksa-Style Chicken & Tofu Noodle Soup with Asian Greens
description: Settle in for a cosy night with this hearty tofu noodle soup. Full of colourful veggies, slurpable noodles and Southeast Asian
flavours, this is the perfect meal to warm you up on a cold night!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/666b9363f9c10e7920c3340d-91e5f84e.jpeg
